<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">ماذا يراد من هذه الأخبار:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>١- <span class="c3">{وَمَا رَبُّكَ بِظَلَّامٍ لِلْعَبِيدِ}</span> ١.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
